[148.057549, "o", "LN(1)                             User Commands                            LN(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       ln - make links between files\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mln\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... [\u001b[4m-T\u001b[24m] \u001b[4mTARGET\u001b[24m \u001b[4mLINK_NAME\u001b[24m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mln\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... \u001b[4mTARGET\u001b[24m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mln\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... \u001b[4mTARGET\u001b[24m... \u001b[4mDIRECTORY\u001b[24m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mln\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m]... \u001b[4m-t\u001b[24m \u001b[4mDIRECTORY\u001b[24m \u001b[4mTARGET\u001b[24m...\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       In the 1st form, create a link to TARGET with the name LINK_NAME.  In the\u001b[m\r\n       2nd form, create a link to TARGET in the current directory.  In  the  3rd\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page ln(1) line 1 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
